title: Tell Sabra
description: Tell in Mesopotamia occupied during the Proto-Dynastic period I, the early Akkadian period, and the Seleuco-Parthian period. Tell Sabra was submerged with the creation of the Hemrin Dam in 1981.

properties.description: Point based on an OpenStreetMap node representing Tell Sabra after Tunca 1987.
properties.title: OSM location of Tell Sabra
